    "name": "水果大乱逗",
    "steam_appid": 3013460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《水果大乱逗》是一款本地聚会游戏，可支持多达9名玩家同乐。其中包含多款极易上手、节奏飞快的小游戏。快叫上朋友和家人，一起享受手忙脚乱的欢乐吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.poster.avif?t=1772200599\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.webm?t=1772200599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/ee906eb86a90f2aa1c514982507892f7.mp4?t=1772200599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操作简单，一键到底</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位玩家都<strong>只需要一个</strong>键，就能参与比拼。<strong>只用一个键</strong>！不用摇杆，鼠标也不用拖动，没错，只要<strong>一</strong>、<strong>个</strong>、<strong>按</strong>、<strong>键</strong>就能玩转。而且，每局游戏开始前都可以重新选择你喜欢的操作方式！无论是鼠标点击、手柄扳机还是空格键……<strong>随你挑</strong>，<strong>统统适用</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.poster.avif?t=1772200599\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.webm?t=1772200599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/4a5a1fafd603b483e5c26363efc24fa9.mp4?t=1772200599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>20款小游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跨栏、切菜、心肺训练、钓鱼……还有更多精彩小游戏等你体验！小游戏各不相同，对技能的要求也<strong>不一样</strong>，所以每位玩家都有机会发挥长处，大放异彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.poster.avif?t=1772200599\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.webm?t=1772200599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/7ed030114e43520aee914793f2ca8ea3.mp4?t=1772200599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>和好友一起在线同玩</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《水果大乱逗》全面支持<strong>Steam远程同乐</strong>功能。只要一人拥有游戏，线上小队成员点几下，就能通过Steam轻松加入，立刻开启欢乐派对！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有需要时，还能共用控制器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聚会手柄不够用？这个游戏没有这种烦恼。如果从开头看到了现在，你就知道，玩这个游戏只用<strong>一个</strong>键。不管是2位、3位，还是9位玩家，都可以用同一个手柄（或键盘）操作！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.poster.avif?t=1772200599\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.webm?t=1772200599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013460/extras/e7810cfdc63726d5e6c94222890be00e.mp4?t=1772200599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
